    161	Key findings:
    162	
    163	(a) **Kt(delta(n)|n) = O(log n) TRIVIALLY**: For any polytime-computable function, Kt = O(1) + log(runtime)
    164	    = O(log n). Kt is NOT the right measure. The correct question is CIRCUIT COMPLEXITY of delta.
